snippet.textDisplay:
I know this company is not into making more affordable cars or some really cool hatchback models but the engine they have has massive amount of power and if he is right about the sound of that engine, they should make a hot hatch only with this engine and that car would be the car of many people I tell you.
Of course with a much more lower price tag but probably still more than 100K+ $ of some kind. I don't know it man, this guy just makes new things from the old concepts and he talks about it like its nothing. 2L, 3-cyl engine that has 600HP is massive news if you ask me. This new tech they have can change how any other car moves on the planet earth right now. I don't know man, I think they should use this engine or this type of tech in more vehicles but not only the super-hyper car market. And the same thing also applies for the 1-gear drive system of the Regera. They use older concepts, but they are much better with better vision of the current times and the future.




I would love to see more commaon models of Koenigsegg in the streets and possibly in races of several kind. That hatchback with that engine would kill the competetion righjt in the moment and they would dominate all kind of races it races. I don't know if that engine is racing legal but if its, they should use it bruh.
